thread.title: Kathleen M Peck
thread.title_full: Munchery reviewed by Kathleen M Peck

author: Kathleen M Peck
title: Kathleen M Peck
text: Chicken is not my favorite meat and the Kalamata olives and roasted red peppers are not usually on my menu for a salad, however this salad was very good; I would most definitely eat this again and have recommended it to my friends and family. Great food for a great price. Thank you!
